title: Introduction Of The New Baja MTZ P3 And The New 2015 Wheels at the 2014 SEMA Show
description: Ben Anderson, of Mickey Thompson Tires, introduces and explains the features and benefits of the Baja MTZ P3 tire.  Carl Robinson, of Mickey Thompson Tires introduces the new wheel line up for 2015, including the 5 new Metal Series models and the Deegan 38 Pro 2 & Pro 4 wheels.
